Agile Grapher
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is a demonstration project to test out the Silex framework in a semi real
world application.

Prerequisites
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sqlite3   ( Tested on 3.7.7-2 ) [ ]
    * sudo apt-get install sqlite3
    * sudo apt-get install php5-sqlite
    * sqlite3 --version

Pear      ( Tested on 1.9.4 )   [ http://pear.php.net ]
    * sudo apt-get install php-pear
    * sudo pear upgrade PEAR

PHPUnit   ( Tested on 3.6 )     [ http://www.phpunit.de ]
    * sudo pear channel-discover pear.phpunit.de
    * sudo apt-get install php-pear
    * sudo pear install pear.phpunit.de/PHPUnit
    * phpunit --version

Phing     ( Tested on 2.4.9 )   [ http://http://www.phing.info ]
    * sudo pear channel-discover pear.phing.info
    * sudo pear install phing/phing
    * phing -version
    
